# set the preferences file prefs="prefs.json"
# first run not completed. Start. if [ ! -d "$nonvolatile" ] then # make the directory mkdir "$nonvolatile" fi

if [ ! -e "$nonvolatile/$prefs" ] then # make the prefs file touch "$nonvolatile/$prefs" fi
# then set the paths python config_find-paths.py
